title: Ex-Apple Engineer Indicted in Crackdown on Flow of Restricted Tech to China, Russia
description: A former Apple engineer has been charged with trying to steal the company’s self-driving-car technology, U.S. authorities said.

title: Venture-Fund Returns Suffer Amid Lower Startup Values
description: The languishing performance of venture-capital funds is denting results for university endowments, pensions and other investors that increased their tech exposure during the bull market.

title: Tesla Board Faces Shareholders Grumpy Over Elon Musk Oversight
description: Former Tesla Chief Technology Officer JB Straubel is up for board election.
